ootswatch 3 themes from here (https://bootswatch.com/3/) -- do we want a lighter theme or a darker theme? I'm currently using `flatly` which seems fine.\r\n\r\nAlso added additional functionality to incorporate notebooks straight into our documentation: \r\n<img width=\"1324\" alt=\"screenshot 2018-05-06 09 59 34\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/761483/39674620-3263baa6-5114-11e8-8a62-3149984731e3.png\">\r\n\r\nand updated the copyright to include my name as one of the authors as well (that ok?).\r\n\r\n# Checklist Before Requesting Approver\r\n\r\n- [X] Tests are passing\r\n- [X] \"WIP\" removed from the title of the pull request\r\n", "created_at": "2018-05-06T15:00:10Z", "updated_at": "2018-05-07T00:04:05Z", "closed_at": "2018-05-06T23:44:33Z", "merged_at": "2018-05-06T23:44:33Z", "merge_commit_sha": "b63effce94132f8894c51f9ed2fa73106f42acd4", "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [{"login": "lukasheinrich", "id": 2318083, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIzMTgwODM=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2318083?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich", "html_url": "https://github.com/lukasheinrich", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lukasheinrich/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": nu